column5: Heading out of the office soon, calling it a year! Probably won't be on the computer for a while, so I thought I'd take a moment here and wish everyone a safe and healthy and happy holiday season! I hope to get out for some perch, if the ice gods allow us to do so, but in any event, have a great holiday everyone! HH
Happy Holidays to you too.  Im outta here for the year as well.  Hope everyone gets what the want for xmas, and all the best in the new year!  Tight lines everyone!
